snippet: Notre Dame’s star big man, Jack Cooley, scored the first 9 points of the game, and the No. 22 Fighting Irish beat Evansville, 58-49, in the Coaches vs. Cancer Classic.
lead_paragraph: Notre Dame’s star big man, Jack Cooley, scored the first 9 points of the game, and the No. 22 Fighting Irish beat Evansville, 58-49, in the Coaches vs. Cancer Classic.

headline.seo: Cooley Leads Notre Dame Past Evansville

headline.print_headline: Cooley Starts Fast for Irish, And Defense Stands Strong
